                    </name>
                    <name>
                        <ln/>
                        <fn/>
                        <sf/>
                        <pf/>
                    </name>
                </names>
                <summary>Responds to a Valley Spirit editorial proclaiming that the county school
                    superintendency is so popular it is virtually unopposed. The Repository begs to
                    differ, and speculates that if an election were held immediately, the
                    superintendency would be turned out.</summary>
                <note/>
            </div>
